creator: Advisor Group, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Royal Alliance eQuipt provides you with an essential solution for monitoring your investments. Stay connected with an intuitive and user-friendly environment designed for easy access while you’re on the go!
With just a few taps, you have access to all of your important account information, including portfolio allocation, cash balances, holdings, historical activity, portfolio valuation over time, and electronic documents and statements. You can even initiate check deposits into your Royal account using the Remote Deposit Capture feature.
Please note:

Investment products are not bank deposits, are not FDIC insured or insured by any federal government agency and may decrease in value. Please contact your financial advisor for details.
descriptionShort: Experience eQuipt: Your roadmap to a well-planned financial future.

title: Royal eQuipt

creator: Osaic, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Stay Connected -

eQuipt provides you with an essential solution for monitoring your investments. Now you can stay connected while you’re on the go—wherever you use your iPhone or iPad. eQuipt lets you view your accounts in an efficient and user-friendly environment that leverages the look and feel of the eQuipt Client Portal, in an app that fits perfectly for the form factor of your tablet or phone.

Through eQuipt, you have fully featured access to account information, such as portfolio allocation, cash balances, holdings, historical activity, portfolio valuation over time, as well as electronic documents and statements. You can also initiate check deposits into your eQuipt account using the Remote Deposit Capture feature.

With just a few clicks from your iPhone or iPad, you can access:

• Account balances and holdings

• Transaction history

• Market information and quotes

• Statements and Documents

Please note:

• Investment products are not bank deposits, are not FDIC insured or insured by any federal government agency and may decrease in value. Please contact your financial advisor for details.
descriptionShort: eQuipt provides essential solution for monitoring investments 24/7 on phone/tab.
